SAPERE API 0.0.1 API

Packages
it.apice.sapere.api This package is the root of all SAPERE system interfaces.
it.apice.sapere.api.ecolaws This package contains the definition of SAPERE Ecolaws and relatives.
it.apice.sapere.api.ecolaws.filters This package contains the definition of SAPERE Ecolaw filters.
it.apice.sapere.api.ecolaws.formulas This package contains the definition of SAPERE Ecolaw's annotated variable's formula.
it.apice.sapere.api.ecolaws.match This package contains the definition of SAPERE Ecolaw matching information.
it.apice.sapere.api.ecolaws.scores This package contains the definition of SAPERE Ecolaw scoring and ranking entities.
it.apice.sapere.api.ecolaws.terms This package contains the definition of SAPERE Ecolaw terms.
it.apice.sapere.api.ecolaws.terms.observers This package contains the definition of SAPERE Ecolaws and relatives (ecolaws.terms.observers).
it.apice.sapere.api.ecolaws.visitor This package contains the definition of an Ecolaw visitor.
it.apice.sapere.api.internal This package contains internal entities that will not be provided outside the bundle.
it.apice.sapere.api.lsas This package contains the definition of a Live Semantic Annotation (LSA) and relatives.
it.apice.sapere.api.lsas.values This package contains the definition of property values supported types.
it.apice.sapere.api.lsas.visitor This package contains the definition of an LSA visitor.
it.apice.sapere.api.space This package contains LSA-space interfaces.
it.apice.sapere.api.space.observation This package contains LSA-space observation features.
